citations:
    citation-acok-davos-i:
        source: source-acok
        properties:
            locator: "Davos I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Davos Seaworth at Dragonstone. Witnesses the burning of the statues of the Seven on the shore. Stannis draws a sword from the fire (claimed to be Lightbringer). Davos's sons Dale, Allard, Matthos, Maric, and Devan are present. Davos meets Salladhor Saan at the inn. Stannis reads his proclamation declaring Cersei and Jaime's incest and his own claim to the Iron Throne. Stannis orders letters sent via ravens to all corners of the realm."
